description: The Magic Door is an Alexa-powered interactive adventure with original stories. You can tell Alexa what choices to make as you navigate a forest, a garden, or an ancient temple. You can find hidden items, solve riddles, and help magical creatures. You can also find magical items to get a prize!
name: The Magic Door
shortDescription: Go on an adventure beyond the magic door. Fairies, gnomes, gods, and treasure await you as you explore the various lands. New: potions and dragons!
